FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772096705
OL,3,CBreastfeeding rooms needed on
OL,4,Cconstruction sites to attract women
OL,5,Cinto jobs
OL,7,FThe Women and Work All Party
OL,8,FParliamentary Group (APPG) 2025
OL,9,FReport, based on a series of sessions
OL,10,Fcarried out last year, was launched in
OL,11,Fparliament today to deliver key
OL,12,Frecommendations on addressing gender
OL,13,Fbalance in the UK economy.
OL,15,FIt noted that women in construction,
OL,16,Finfrastructure and other non-office
OL,17,Fworkplaces face a number of practical
OL,18,Fbarriers, including "inadequate
OL,19,Ffacilities", that undermine their
OL,20,Fparticipation and wellbeing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772096705
OL,3,CBreastfeeding rooms needed on
OL,4,Cconstruction sites to attract women
OL,5,Cinto jobs
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,F"These basic shortcomings contribute
OL,13,Fto feelings of exclusion and hinder
OL,14,Fretention," the report said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772096705
OL,3,CBreastfeeding rooms needed on
OL,4,Cconstruction sites to attract women
OL,5,Cinto jobs
OL,7,FIt recommended embedding gender
OL,8,Finclusion standards into public
OL,9,Fprocurement, so that companies hoping
OL,10,Fto win government infrastructure or
OL,11,Fenergy contracts are forced to
OL,12,Fdemonstrate inclusive facilities and
OL,13,Fpractices.
OL,15,FThe report also stated that employers
OL,16,Fmust have independent reporting
OL,17,Fmechanisms for workplace harassment
OL,18,Fwith clear accountability standards,
OL,19,Fso women feel safe enough to report
OL,20,Fincidents without risk to their career.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772096705
OL,3,CBreastfeeding rooms needed on
OL,4,Cconstruction sites to attract women
OL,5,Cinto jobs
OL,7,F"Encouraging women's participation in
OL,8,Fwork is not only a matter of fairness,
OL,9,Fbut of economic necessity," said
OL,10,FBaroness Karren Brady, co-chair of the
OL,11,FWomen and Work APPG, in the report's
OL,12,Fforeword.
OL,14,F"Women bring talent, leadership,
OL,15,Finnovation, and diverse perspectives
OL,16,Fthat strengthen organisations, drive
OL,17,Fproductivity, and underpin sustainable
OL,18,Fgrowth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772096705
OL,3,CBreastfeeding rooms needed on
OL,4,Cconstruction sites to attract women
OL,5,Cinto jobs
OL,7,F"Failing to fully harness this
OL,8,Fpotential is a loss not only to women,
OL,9,Fbut to the wider economy and society
OL,10,Fas a whole."
OL,12,FThe government should set out a
OL,13,Fwomen's skills strategy ensuring
OL,14,Faccess to expertise needed in AI,
OL,15,Fdigital, and engineering professions,
OL,16,Fthe report advised.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
