OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772096705
OL,3,CBreastfeeding rooms needed on
OL,4,Cconstruction sites to attract women
OL,5,Cinto jobs
OL,7,FIt stated that early exposure to STEM
OL,8,Fsubjects was essential to attracting
OL,9,Fwomen and girls to such professions,
OL,10,Fand recommended funding early
OL,11,Fintervention programmes to create
OL,12,Faccess to female role models,
OL,13,Fmentoring, and hands-on experiences
OL,14,Ffrom primary school onwards.
OL,16,FAlmost 70% of STEM students in higher
OL,17,Feducation are male, recent data from
OL,18,Fthe Higher Education Statistics Agency
OL,19,Fshows.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
