OL,3,CBreastfeeding rooms needed on
OL,4,Cconstruction sites to attract women
OL,5,Cinto jobs
OL,7,FThe report also stated that gendered
OL,8,Fabuse poses a growing threat to female
OL,9,Fparticipation in public life, with
OL,10,Fwomen encountering abuse online and
OL,11,Foffline across politics, media,
OL,12,Fbusiness and sport.
OL,14,FIt called for stronger regulation of
OL,15,Fsocial media, as well as
OL,16,Faccountability from the platforms
OL,17,Fwhere abuse takes place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
